quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  23,105,kiya tum ko meri ayatain parh kar nahi sunai jatein theen ( nahi ) tum un ko suntay they ( aur ) jutlatay they
  23,106,ae hamaray perwar-digaar! hum par hamari kam bakhti ghalib hogayi aur hum raste se bhatak gay
  23,107,"ae perwar-digaar! hum ko is mein se nikaal day, agar hum phir ( aisay kaam ) karen to zalim hon ge"
  23,108,( khuda ) farmaiye ga ke isi mein zillat ke sath parre raho aur mujh se baat nah karo
  23,109,mere bundon mein aik giroh tha jo duakiya karta tha ke ae hamaray perwar-digaar hum imaan laaye to too hum ko bakhash day aur hum par reham kar aur to sab se behtar reham karne wala hai
  23,110,to tum un se tamaskhur karte rahay yahan taq ke un ke peechay meri yaad bhi bhool gay aur tum ( hamesha ) un se hansikiya karte they
  23,111,"aaj mein ne unn ko unn ke sabr ka badla diya, ke woh kamyaab hogaye"
  23,112,( khuda ) pouchye ga ke tum zameen mein kitney baras rahay ?
  23,113,"woh kahin ge ke hum aik roz ya aik roz se bhi kam rahay they, shumaar karne walon se pooch lijiye"
  23,114,( khuda ) farmaiye ga ke ( wahan ) tum ( bohat hi ) kam rahay. kash tum jantay hotay
  23,115,kiya tum yeh khayaal karte ho ke hum ne tum ko be faida pedakiya hai aur yeh tum hamari taraf lout kar nahi aao ge ?
  23,116,"to khuda jo sacha badshah hai ( is ki shaan ) is se onche hai, is ke siwa koi mabood nahi, wohi arsh buzurag ka maalik hai"
  23,117,aur jo shakhs khuda ke sath aur mabood ko pukaarta hai jis ki is ke paas kuch bhi sanad nahi to is ka hisaab khuda hi ke haan hoga. kuch shak nahi ke kafir rstgari nahi payen ge
  23,118,aur khuda se dua karo ke mere perwar-digaar mujhe bakhash day aur ( mujh par ) reham kar aur to sab se behtar reham karne wala hai
